lead_paragraph: Cristiano Ronaldo continued his rich vein of form by scoring twice in Real Madrid's 2-1 home win over struggling Sporting Gijon on Saturday, although the La Liga leaders got a lucky break when the visitors squandered a second-half penalty.

headline.print_headline: Ronaldo Double as Real Ride Luck to Beat Sporting
